title: Hawkwind 1973-02-24 Dusseldorf SPACE RITUAL -FLAC
description:
The Space Ritual tour hits Germany! Lots of familaiar effects and lots of unfamiliar bits too.

Quality: 7. A bit rough, but quite listenable. I think this is the best quality audience recording of the Space Ritual tour that currently exists.

This show has also been made available in MP3 form.

Remaster CDR ? > Amadeus II EQ > Flac level 5
